question.title: Jenv setup with non-existing bin folder
question.body:
I am referring this https://www.jenv.be/ Which includes a step to add ".jenv/bin" to PATH. My question is on the steps mentioned here

$ echo 'export PATH="$HOME/.jenv/bin:$PATH"' >> ~/.zshrc
$ echo 'eval "$(jenv init -)"' >> ~/.zshrc

Since no such executable or directory named "bin" exists under .jenv directory (shims and versions directories do exist) whats the purpose of adding it to PATH?
